#. <section class="sutta" id="sn56.131"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn56.131:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 56"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 56"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn56.131:0.2"
msgid "11. Pañcagatipeyyālavagga"
msgstr "11. Abbreviated Texts on Five Destinations"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn56.131:0.3"
msgid "131. Pettidevapettivisayasutta"
msgstr "131. Dying as Ghosts and Reborn as Ghosts"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn56.131:1.1"
msgid "… “Evameva kho, bhikkhave, appakā te sattā ye pettivisayā cutā devesu paccājāyanti; atha kho eteva bahutarā sattā ye pettivisayā cutā pettivisaye paccājāyanti."
msgstr "“… the sentient beings who die as ghosts and are reborn as gods are few, while those who die as ghosts and are reborn in the ghost realm are many."

msgctxt "sn56.131:1.2"
msgid "Taṃ kissa hetu?"
msgstr "Why is that?"

msgctxt "sn56.131:1.3"
msgid "Adiṭṭhattā, bhikkhave, catunnaṃ ariyasaccānaṃ."
msgstr "It’s because they haven’t seen the four noble truths."

msgctxt "sn56.131:1.4"
msgid "Katamesaṃ catunnaṃ?"
msgstr "What four?"

msgctxt "sn56.131:1.5"
msgid "Dukkhassa ariyasaccassa, dukkhasamudayassa ariyasaccassa, dukkhanirodhassa ariyasaccassa, dukkhanirodhagāminiyā paṭipadāya ariyasaccassa."
msgstr "The noble truths of suffering, the origin of suffering, the cessation of suffering, and the practice that leads to the cessation of suffering."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "sn56.131:2.1"
msgid "Tasmātiha, bhikkhave, ‘idaṃ dukkhan’ti yogo karaṇīyo, ‘ayaṃ dukkhasamudayo’ti yogo karaṇīyo, ‘ayaṃ dukkhanirodho’ti yogo karaṇīyo, ‘ayaṃ dukkhanirodhagāminī paṭipadā’ti yogo karaṇīyo”ti."
msgstr "That’s why you should practice meditation to understand: ‘This is suffering’ … ‘This is the origin of suffering’ … ‘This is the cessation of suffering’ … ‘This is the practice that leads to the cessation of suffering’.”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "sn56.131:3.1"
msgid "Idamavoca bhagavā."
msgstr "That is what the Buddha said."

msgctxt "sn56.131:3.2"
msgid "Attamanā te bhikkhū bhagavato bhāsitaṃ abhinandunti."
msgstr "Satisfied, the mendicants were happy with what the Buddha said."

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn56.131:3.3"
msgid "Tiṃsatimaṃ."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn56.131:3.4"
msgid "Pañcagatipeyyālavaggo ekādasamo."
msgstr ""

#. </p><blockquote class="uddanagatha"><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "sn56.131:4.1"
msgid "Manussato cutā chāpi,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn56.131:4.2"
msgid "devā cutā nirayato;"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn56.131:4.3"
msgid "Tiracchānapettivisayā,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn56.131:4.4"
msgid "tiṃsamatto gativaggoti."
msgstr ""

#. </p></blockquote><p class="endsutta">
msgctxt "sn56.131:4.5"
msgid "Saccasaṃyuttaṃ dvādasamaṃ."
msgstr "The Linked Discourses on the Truths, the twelfth section."

#. </p><p class="endsutta">
msgctxt "sn56.131:4.6"
msgid "Mahāvaggo pañcamo."
msgstr ""

#. </p><blockquote class="uddanagatha"><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli5.478"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc5"></a>
msgctxt "sn56.131:5.1"
msgid "Maggabojjhaṅgaṃ satiyā,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn56.131:5.2"
msgid "indriyaṃ sammappadhānaṃ;"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn56.131:5.3"
msgid "Baliddhipādānuruddhā,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn56.131:5.4"
msgid "jhānānāpānasaṃyutaṃ;"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn56.131:5.5"
msgid "Sotāpatti saccañcāti,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn56.131:5.6"
msgid "mahāvaggoti vuccatīti."
msgstr ""

#. </p></blockquote><p class="endbook">
msgctxt "sn56.131:5.7"
msgid "Mahāvaggasaṃyuttapāḷi niṭṭhitā."
msgstr "The Great Book is finished."

#. </p><p class="endbook">
msgctxt "sn56.131:5.8"
msgid "Saṃyuttanikāyo samatto."
msgstr "The Linked Discourses is completed."
